songs.title: Call To Nevaeh
songs.lyrics:
[Skit]
Yeah, waddup?
Don't even, don't even talk, let me–
Let me explain
I know I've been missin' for a while, [?]
Don't worry, everything is cool, everything is good
I just been eh– I needed to find myself
Sometime I need to know something, babe
And that's just what I did
To help me pass away
Ehm
The time to go
I appreciate you, I really, I really do
I been to nothing but drinkin' and thinkin', yeah
Everything [?] at the right time, yeah
PinkElephants
